title: War of the Roses: She Wants What Kind of Tattoo?
description: Logan is suspicious her boyfriend is cheating and she tries to trap him in a very unique way, by telling him a tattoo she wants that she saw on the girl she thinks he's cheating on her with.  See if he thinks the tattoo is  a good idea and if not, does that mean he's cheating?
